OL,3,CFirearms trainers at the National
OL,4,CCrime Agency sacked for faking records
OL,6,FFive firearms trainers at the National
OL,7,FCrime Agency (NCA) have been sacked
OL,8,Fafter it was found they faked official
OL,9,Frecords.
OL,11,FThe group were all ruled to have
OL,12,Fcommitted gross misconduct after an
OL,13,Finternal investigation into claims
OL,14,Fthey had falsified records linked to
OL,15,Ffirearms training between December
OL,16,F2021 and July 2022, the NCA said.
