OL,3,CFirearms trainers at the National
OL,4,CCrime Agency sacked for faking records
OL,6,FOne of the sacked officers had been
OL,7,Fdue to be called as a prosecution
OL,8,Fwitness in a separate trial at
OL,9,FLiverpool Crown Court where an NCA
OL,10,Fofficer was accused of two counts of
OL,11,Fmisconduct in public office.
OL,13,FProsecutors decided not to pursue the
OL,14,Fcase after the witness was sacked.
OL,16,FAnother three trainers resigned from
OL,17,Ftheir jobs before they could face
OL,18,Fdisciplinary hearings.
