OL,3,CFirearms trainers at the National
OL,4,CCrime Agency sacked for faking records
OL,6,FTwo would have been sacked and the
OL,7,Fthird would have been given a written
OL,8,Fwarning if they had still been in
OL,9,Fpost, the NCA found.
OL,11,FNCA deputy director Nigel Leary, said:
OL,12,F"The NCA expects the highest standards
OL,13,Fof integrity and conduct from its
OL,14,Fofficers.
OL,16,F"Our mission is to protect the public
OL,17,Ffrom serious and organised crime, and
OL,18,Fit is important that we do this with
OL,19,Fthe support and confidence of the
OL,20,Fpeople we serve.
