OL,3,CFirearms trainers at the National
OL,4,CCrime Agency sacked for faking records
OL,6,F"To do this effectively it is
OL,7,Fessential that we root out misconduct
OL,8,Fand ensure we only ever have the right
OL,9,Fpeople working for us."
OL,11,FThe Liverpool Crown Court case was
OL,12,Flinked to allegations of corruption
OL,13,Fagainst an NCA officer in October
OL,14,F2018, who resigned from his job in May
OL,15,F2019.
OL,17,FThe NCA is now considering whether to
OL,18,Fbring disciplinary proceedings after
OL,19,Fthe prosecution was withdrawn.
